# Pure Module
#
# Pure functional utilities (28 files).
# Provides side-effect-free functions for common operations.
#
# Categories:
#   - Array operations
#   - String manipulation
#   - Math utilities
#   - Functional programming helpers
#   - Data transformations
#
# Public API:
#   - All functions are public (pure utilities)
#   - Import: use std.pure.{function_name}

# All submodules are automatically available.
# This is the largest library module with comprehensive utility functions.

